document_data.name: House Higure
document_data.mainbody: '''House Higure''' was one of the ruling [[drow]] Houses of [[Menzoberranzan]] in the [[Northdark]] in the late 14{{th}} and 15{{th}} centuries [[DR]].
document_data.History: House Higure rose to its [[Ruling Council]] status sometime after the {{YearlinkName|1358}} and before the {{YearlinkName|1372}}, when it was the seventeenth House of Menzoberranzan. By the {{YearlinkName|1480}}, House Higure climbed up to claim its place as the thirteenth House of Menzoberranzan.
